{"title":"Alpitude Stelvio Corretto is World’s Lightest Out-Front GPS Computer Mount from 12.9g!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/alpitude-stelvio-corretto-worlds-lightest-ultralight-carbon-out-front-gps-mount/","date":1691584146000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_new-truss-profile.jpg\" alt=\"Alpitude Stelvio Corretto ultralight carbon out-front GPS cycling computer mount for road bike 1-piece integrated handlebar cockpits, truss profile\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_new-truss-profile.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_new-truss-profile-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_new-truss-profile-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_new-truss-profile-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_new-truss-profile-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_new-truss-profile-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_new-truss-profile-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Alpitude Stelvio <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=alpitude+Stelvio\" target=\"_blank\">cycling computer mounts</a> have been some of the lightest for years, but their newest full-carbon Stelvio Corretto claims to be a new World’s lightest. An out-front mount developed for the growing crop of integrated 1-piece bars from ~13-15g (in both universal fit &amp; bar-specific versions), the new Stelvio Corretto is also the lightest combo mount that can carry a headlight or camera too for just 3g extra…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Alpitude Stelvio Corretto ultralight carbon out-front mount</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_up-close.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_up-close.jpg\" alt=\"Alpitude Stelvio Corretto ultralight carbon out-front GPS cycling computer mount for road bike 1-piece integrated handlebar cockpits, up close\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_up-close.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_up-close-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_up-close-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_up-close-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_up-close-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_up-close-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_up-close-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>all photos c. Alpitude</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Six years after their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/eb17-alpitude-lightweight-carbon-stelvio-front-gps-mount-ultra-bottle-cage/\" target=\"_blank\">first lightweight GPS mount</a> and five years after their first integrated bar mount, Alpitude’s newest Stelvio Corretto drops the box shape for a lighter &amp; 38% stronger full-carbon truss. At the same time, it retains Alpitude’s proven (and patented) open 4-bolt head design that works with inserts for the most popular cycling computers, plus a removable GoPro-style bracket to mount additional out-front accessories.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_undeside-detail.jpg\"><img width=\"1200\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_undeside-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Alpitude Stelvio Corretto ultralight carbon out-front GPS cycling computer mount for road bike 1-piece integrated handlebar cockpits, underside detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_undeside-detail.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_undeside-detail-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_undeside-detail-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_undeside-detail-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_undeside-detail-768x461.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Handcrafted in the Dolomites of northern Italy from hi-mod T700 &amp; T800S carbon fiber with new high-pressure molding, the Alpitude Stelvio Corretto features a new stiffer hollow ‘folded truss’ design to support large-sized cycling computers. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_GoPro-accessory-mount.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_GoPro-accessory-mount.jpg\" alt=\"Alpitude Stelvio Corretto ultralight carbon out-front GPS cycling computer mount for road bike 1-piece integrated handlebar cockpits, GoPro mount\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_GoPro-accessory-mount.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_GoPro-accessory-mount-297x165.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_GoPro-accessory-mount-800x444.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_GoPro-accessory-mount-120x67.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_GoPro-accessory-mount-768x427.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_GoPro-accessory-mount-1536x853.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And thanks to Alpitude’s ultralight 3g pass-through carbon loop hanger, it can also support a lightweight headlight or action camera, too. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Alpitude Stelvio Corretto – Pricing, Options &amp; Compatibility</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_options.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_options.jpg\" alt=\"Alpitude Stelvio Corretto ultralight carbon out-front GPS cycling computer mount for road bike 1-piece integrated handlebar cockpits, options\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_options.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_options-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_options-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_options-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_options-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_options-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_options-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Alpitude Stelvio Corretto is available in 7 different versions to fit the majority of integrated 1-piece stem+bars on the market for 110€, or for 130€ with the GoPro-style combo adapter mount. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_universal.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_universal.jpg\" alt=\"Alpitude Stelvio Corretto ultralight carbon out-front GPS cycling computer mount for road bike 1-piece integrated handlebar cockpits, universal mount\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_universal.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_universal-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_universal-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_universal-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_universal-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_universal-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_universal-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Universal model fits: FSA Plasma, PRO Stealth Evo, Cinelli RAM 2, Chapter 2 Mana, Ritchey WCS Solostream &amp; Darimo <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/is-darimo-nexum-worlds-lightest-carbon-road-bike-cockpit-handlebar-stem-combo-at-195g/\" target=\"_blank\">Nexum</a> bars (14.5g). Or there are handlebar-specific models to fit the BMC <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/bmc-teammachine-slr-mpc-aero-road-bike-masterpiece/\" target=\"_blank\">SLR</a> 01(15g), Cannondale <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/cannondale-evo-road-bike-lab71-15k/\" target=\"_blank\">LAB71</a> System Bar (12.9g), Cervélo <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2023-cervelo-s5-aero-road-bike-drops-drag-with-subtle-reshaping/\" target=\"_blank\">S5</a> HB14 (13g for small computers, 14.2g for large devices), Pinarello F <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/pinarello-stepping-their-most-cockpit-components-up-to-the-team-sky-big-league/\" target=\"_blank\">Most Talon</a> Ultra (20g), THM <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/thms-new-299g-clavicula-xc-mountain-bike-cranks-222g-1-piece-road-cockpit-ultralight-schmolke-bars/\" target=\"_blank\">Frontale</a> (15.5g), Vision Metron <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/eb18-vision-wheels-see-road-tubeless-updates-plus-compact-aero-cranks-more/\" target=\"_blank\">5D/6D</a> ACR (18g). Alpitude can also custom-make their Stelvio Corretto to fit other bar standards on request.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>All weights are claimed by Alpitude +/-5%, excluding mounting bolts.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_1-piece-cockpit-compatiblity-options.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_1-piece-cockpit-compatiblity-options.jpg\" alt=\"Alpitude Stelvio Corretto ultralight carbon out-front GPS cycling computer mount for road bike 1-piece integrated handlebar cockpits, options\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_1-piece-cockpit-compatiblity-options.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_1-piece-cockpit-compatiblity-options-297x165.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_1-piece-cockpit-compatiblity-options-800x444.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_1-piece-cockpit-compatiblity-options-120x67.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_1-piece-cockpit-compatiblity-options-768x427.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Alpitude-Stelvio-Corretto-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-direct-integrated-mount_1-piece-cockpit-compatiblity-options-1536x853.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Stelvio Correttos can be purchased in ‘small’ length to fit GPS cycling computers up to 80mm long, or ‘normal’ length to fit larger devices as well. Pick from Garmin, Wahoo, or Polar device compatibility with replaceable mounting plates.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All are available to order direct from Alpitude, with 1-2 week estimated shipping dates, or via their select global dealer network.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://alpitude.cc/\" target=\"_blank\">Alpitude.cc</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/alpitude-stelvio-corretto-worlds-lightest-ultralight-carbon-out-front-gps-mount/\">Alpitude Stelvio Corretto is World’s Lightest Out-Front GPS Computer Mount from 12.9g!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"36f8ba70ecef836748d1dfeffeb0bd3bc4bd5be6ebc21af194135de30a7eaaba","category":"Cycling"}